{"name":"Fireball","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-orange-yellow.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3diTdVzEbSQ8zLoi"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Arcane, Tier 2 &bull; Fire</strong></p>\n<p><em>With a wave of your hand, a brilliant sphere of energy erupts from your catalyst, streaking towards your target before detonating with a dull roar.<br></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Range </strong>Burst 3 within 30<br><strong>Difficulty </strong>4<br><strong>Cost </strong>2 Increments<br><strong>AP </strong>2<br><strong>Resistance </strong>Yes (Dodge 4)<br><strong>Effect</strong> <em>On hit: </em>All creatures and objects within the burst take 200% Thermal damage. Flammable objects within the target area catch fire; all creatures take ongoing 5/T Thermal damage (save ends).</p>","cost":2,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":2},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774473580023,"modifiedTime":1774473580023,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"K0YxhMnmfTl0NrDw"}
{"name":"Flamethrower","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/fire/beam-jet-stream-trails-orange.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.N4icdxmLISJhtDzx"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Arcane Spell &bull; Tier 1 &bull; Fire</strong></p>\n<p>Difficulty: 2<br>Cost: 1 Increment<br>Targets: Cone 10<br>Saving Throw: Yes (Dodge vs Arcane Check)</p>\n<p>Effect: All creatures and objects within the cone take 100% Thermal damage. <span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b0820897-7fff-3262-bb97-544a46e3c03b\">All flammable objects within the area of the spell catch fire. All targets struck take ongoing 3/T Thermal damage (save ends</span><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b0820897-7fff-3262-bb97-544a46e3c03b\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">).</span></p>","cost":1,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":1},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774473581255,"modifiedTime":1774473581255,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"nJn3esUyWZhFObV1"}
{"name":"Solar Flare","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-wave-arrow.webp","system":{"tier":4,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 4 Arcane Spell &bull; Fire</strong></p>\n<p><em>You stretch out your hand and cast a wave of blazing plasma, bathing all before you in the fury of a burning star. </em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Range&nbsp;</strong>Line 15<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>8<br><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>3 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>3<br><strong>Armor&nbsp;</strong>Yes<br><strong>Resistance&nbsp;</strong>Yes&nbsp;<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>All creatures and objects within the line take 300% Thermal damage. Additionally, all targets must make a D 9 Stamina resist; on failure, they lose 3/T armor/hardness. Flammable objects and living targets reduced to 0 Health by this power turn to ash. Objects reduced to zero hardness by this power melt or disintegrate.</p>","cost":3,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":3},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.MxfDvyZgZCekeJUD"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767447473095,"modifiedTime":1774473582921,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"JcsgPkwYOHNvHjEu"}
{"name":"Ice Storm","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/water/vortex-water-whirlpool.webp","system":{"tier":4,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Arcane Spell, Tier 3 &bull; Ice, Wind</strong></p>\n<p><em>Temperatures start to drop precipitously as a whirlwind picks up. The storm lasts only a few seconds, leaving everything covered in a sheet of glistening ice.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Range&nbsp;</strong>Burst 5 within 20<br><strong>Difficulty </strong>8<br><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>3 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>3<br><strong>Armor&nbsp;</strong>Yes<br><strong>Resistance&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Stamina 6)<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>All targets within the range take 200% cold damage and must make a D6 Stamina resist. On failure, they are stunned for one round; afterwards, they are dazed and slowed (5) (save ends).</p>","cost":3,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":2},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4opYB83RiHwHPqgL"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767458802047,"modifiedTime":1774473585215,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"tEGcyq0SNR3EdbZb"}
{"name":"Fulmination","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-explosion-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.QpDlYQkVJjCIXlJi"}},"system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Arcane, Tier 3 &bull; Lightning</strong></p>\n<p><em>For a split second, hair stands on end and the air crackles with anticipation before a terrifying burst of electrical energy discharges from your catalyst, sending bolts of brilliant blue plasma tearing into every foe unfortunate enough to stand close to you.</em></p>\n<p><em><br></em><strong>Range</strong> Close Burst 5; all enemies within burst<br><strong>Difficulty </strong>6<br><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>3 Increments<br><strong>AP </strong>3<br><strong>Resistance </strong>Yes (Stamina 6)<br><strong>Armor&nbsp;</strong>No<br><strong>Effect <br></strong><em>On hit:</em><em> </em>200% electric damage, and the target is stunned for one round. <br><em>Miss: </em>Half damage and the target is dazed instead.</p>","cost":3,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":2},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774473587747,"modifiedTime":1774473587747,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"jcozirpcFGQOVo0H"}
{"name":"Lightning Bolt","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-blue-white.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.JEOCQqLjLPHhFs5a"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Arcane, Tier 1 &bull; Lightning</strong></p>\n<p><em>You raise your catalyst, and with a deafening peal of thunder, a bolt of lightning erupts from it to smite your enemies.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Range </strong>Line 10<br /><strong>Difficulty </strong>3<br /><strong>Cost </strong>1 Increment<br /><strong>AP </strong>2<br /><strong>Resistance </strong>Yes (Stamina 3)<br /><strong>Effect</strong><br /><em>On hit: </em>100% electric damage vs MArm, and the target is stunned for one round.</p>","cost":0,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774473589529,"modifiedTime":1774473589529,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"tnqJ5dy7XmV9FDHu"}
{"name":"Forest of Corpses","type":"power","img":"icons/skills/melee/spear-tips-quintuple-orange.webp","system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Unique Power, Tier 6 &bull; Weapon</strong></p>\n<p><em>You thrust Kazykly deep into the earth. For a second, everything is silent, before sharpened stakes of solid shadow erupt beneath your enemies. Blood and guts run over the stakes, your grim work leaving nothing but a forest of corpses.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Range&nbsp;</strong>Close Burst 10<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>7<br><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>3 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>3<br><strong>Armor</strong> Yes<br><strong>Resistance&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Stamina 8)<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>Every creature targeted by this power must take a Dive reaction to avoid the stake (Dodge DC equal to this power's attack roll). On failure, it takes 300% piercing damage and is&nbsp;<em>immobilized</em>; in addition, it must make a&nbsp;D8 Stamina check or be stunned for one round. On each of the target's turns, it must make a D6 Athletics check to vault off the stake or take 100% damage and remain immobilized. <br><strong>Special&nbsp;</strong>If you fail the attack roll to invoke this power,&nbsp;<em>Kazykly&nbsp;</em>becomes stuck in the ground. Pulling it back out is a 1AP action and requires a successful D7 Martial check.</p>","cost":3,"subType":"uniquePower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"meleeWeapon","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"martial","damageMultiplier":3},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.tAxo22K7IFtiM4id"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768048192735,"modifiedTime":1774473602659,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"Q8AhnDEvf9eAMAF2"}
{"name":"Wounds from Nowhere","type":"power","img":"icons/skills/melee/blade-tip-energy-green.webp","system":{"tier":5,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 5 Innate Power (Psychic) &bull; Void</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites&nbsp;</strong>You must be wielding the <em>Void</em> <em>Blade<br></em><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>2 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>2<br><strong>Range&nbsp;</strong>1 within 15<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>7<br><strong>Armor</strong> &nbsp;No, Ward applies<br><strong>Resist&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Potential 8)&nbsp;<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>The Void Blade disappears from your hands, striking at the enemy's vulnerable innards. The target must make a D8 Potential save; on failure, it takes 300% damage, ignoring armor. On success: it takes 100% damage. Whether the check fails or succeeds, the <em>Void Blade </em>cannot be used until the end of your next turn after you attempt to manifest this power, when it returns to your hand.</p>","cost":2,"subType":"legendaryPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"meleeWeapon","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":3},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.MIOUqCWGwuhNNdth"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1770501415246,"modifiedTime":1774473604467,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"HrxdZAxT8WmDcyeW"}
{"name":"Lotus Art: Impenetrable","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-blue-yellow.webp","system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 1 Exploit &bull; Lotus Art, Stance</strong></p>\n<p><em>\"The true sage does not seek to counter strength with strength, but redirects it. The blade runs off him like water off a lotus leaf.\"</em></p>\n<p><strong>Cost:</strong> --<br><strong>AP:&nbsp;</strong>1<br><strong>Sustain:&nbsp;</strong>1<br><strong>Effect:</strong> While in <em>Impenetrable</em> stance, you gain a +2 bonus to your Evasion.&nbsp;</p>","cost":0,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.iwNrqfE3cUEQYr4P"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767464467381,"modifiedTime":1774473615446,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"arCUxMPWcYb0Y5qT"}
{"name":"Lotus Art: Noble Eightfold Blade","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-orange-purple.webp","system":{"tier":5,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 5 Exploit &bull; Lotus Art, Dual Wield</strong></p>\n<p><em>\"The master said: there are eight worlds in creation. To truly kill your enemy, you must cut him down in each of them.\"</em></p>\n<p><strong>Cost:&nbsp;</strong>3 Increments<br><strong>AP</strong>: 3<br><strong>Range</strong>: Weapon<br><strong>Difficulty:</strong> Special<br><strong>Armor: </strong>Half<br><strong>Resistance: </strong>Yes (Potential 9)<br><strong>Prerequisites:&nbsp;</strong>You must be wielding two bladed weapons<br><strong>Effect: </strong>&nbsp;When you perform this exploit, you may make four attacks, against the same or different targets. The difficulty of the first attack is equal to the target's evasion, increasing by 2 on each subsequent attack, up to +6 on the fourth one. Each attack deals 100% damage at half armor.&nbsp;<br><em>Secondary: </em>After performing all attacks, targets hit must make a D9 Potential check. On failure, they suffer the following effects, depending on how many times they were hit (these effects stack):</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 95px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 44.294%;\"><col style=\"width: 55.5126%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\"><strong>Number of Hits</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\"><strong>Effect</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\">The target is&nbsp;<em>stilled.</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\">The target loses 5 EP.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\">3&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\">The target is&nbsp;<em>exposed.</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"height: 19px;\">The target dies instantly and loses 5 more EP.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","cost":0,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1qfkqdHyS1tnLkpJ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769814411752,"modifiedTime":1774473617469,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"9lESLiN97Qq8ie0C"}
{"name":"Lotus Art: Pearl Scissor","type":"power","img":"icons/skills/melee/weapons-crossed-swords-black.webp","system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 3 Martial Exploit &bull; Lotus Art, Dual Wield</strong></p>\n<p><em>The honed blade cuts the line of the soul.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>2 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>2<br><strong>Range&nbsp;</strong>Line, Movement Range<br><strong>Difficulty</strong> 5<br><strong>Prerequisites&nbsp;</strong>You must be wielding two bladed weapons.<br><strong>Armor&nbsp;</strong>Partial<br><strong>Resist&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Dodge 6)<br><strong>Effect</strong> All targets on the line are hit once by each wielded weapon, halving armor.&nbsp;<em>Secondary:&nbsp;</em>The target must make a D8 Potential save; on failure: it is&nbsp;<em>stilled&nbsp;</em>(save ends).</p>","cost":2,"subType":"martialPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"meleeWeapon","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"martial","damageMultiplier":1},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lPVoDc1uX2Eehtiv"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767464281117,"modifiedTime":1774473619301,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"0MX3LhE7TZPEp3NQ"}
{"name":"Lotus Art: Pure Land Burial","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/death/grave-tombstone-glow-teal.webp","system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 2 Exploit &bull; Lotus Art</strong></p>\n<p><em>Every soul yearns to return to the soil of the Pure Land from which it was born. This blade will show it the way.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Cost:&nbsp;</strong>1 Increment<br><strong>AP:&nbsp;</strong>2<br><strong>Difficulty:&nbsp;</strong>+2<br><strong>Range:&nbsp;</strong>Weapon<br><strong>Prerequisites: -&nbsp;<br>Effect:&nbsp;</strong>On hit: the target takes 200% damage. <br><em>Secondary:</em> The target must make a D6 Potential resist. On failure: the target loses 5 EP, if applicable.<br>A target killed by this power must make a D8 Potential resist each round it is dead. On failure, it cannot revive or be revived that turn. This power does not prevent discorporation.</p>","cost":1,"subType":"martialExploit","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"meleeWeapon","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"martial","damageMultiplier":2},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PnZ7lnaqaT6s6ueA"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767464302615,"modifiedTime":1774473620955,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"cN0DBiN63j7yaQlf"}
{"name":"Lotus Art: Thousand Petal","type":"power","img":"icons/skills/melee/blade-tips-triple-bent-white.webp","system":{"tier":4,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 4 Exploit &bull; Lotus Art, Dual Wield</strong></p>\n<p><em>When the creator made the universe, it is said that he first made a lotus flower of a thousand petals, and when he scattered the petals, from each one there blossomed a world.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong> You must be wielding two bladed weapons<br><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>2 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>3<br><strong>Range</strong> Close Burst 5<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>7<br><strong>Resistance</strong> Yes (Dive; Dodge 8)<br><strong>Armor </strong>Half<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>On hit: the target takes 100% damage, halving armor. The target must also make a D7 Potential save; on failure: it loses 2 EP.</p>","cost":2,"subType":"martialExploit","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"meleeWeapon","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"martial","damageMultiplier":1},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.V9NKTRsUVntgneVG"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767464291986,"modifiedTime":1774473622826,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"QniUyouZbTLphLsB"}
{"name":"Reversal of Fortune","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-power.webp","system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Psychic Power, Tier 2 &bull; Fate</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>2 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>2<br><strong>Range</strong> 1 within 12<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>6<br><strong>Resist&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Potential 5)<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>On the target's next roll, all 6s count as 1 success.<br><strong>Augment 2&nbsp;</strong>You may use this power as a reaction.</p>","cost":2,"subType":"psychicPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.FmCghCodULmj9Co0"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769871995596,"modifiedTime":1774473629513,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"xDIFqE4qYr5Z1sJQ"}
{"name":"Twist of Fate","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/symbols/star-solid-gold.webp","system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Psychic Power, Tier 1 &bull; Fate, Reaction</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>1 Increment<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>2<br><strong>Difficulty</strong> 5<br><strong>Range&nbsp;</strong>1 within 12<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>On the target's next roll, you may modify the result by +1 or -1.&nbsp;<br><strong>Augment 2</strong>&nbsp;You may use this power as a reaction.</p>","cost":1,"subType":"psychicPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3xfk7cqekoHvEzDX"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769871984715,"modifiedTime":1774473631274,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"14rYzJHVM8cSr8l2"}
{"name":"Cursed Fate, Mass","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/death/skull-energy-light-white.webp","system":{"tier":5,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Psychic Power, Tier 5 &bull; Fate, Curse</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Cost </strong>3&nbsp;Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>3<br><strong>Range</strong> Burst 5 within 20; all enemies in burst<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>10<br><strong>Duration&nbsp;</strong>Save ends<br><strong>Resist&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Potential 8)<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>For the duration of the effect, all 1s count as -2 successes, rather than -1.&nbsp;<br><strong>Augment 2&nbsp;</strong>Saving against this effect requires 3 successes.&nbsp;</p>","cost":3,"subType":"psychicPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Hvyo5ahumA9iV8jK"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1770500759223,"modifiedTime":1774473632942,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"f3a2B2y1vQPYiNYy"}
{"name":"Cursed Fate","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/death/skull-energy-light-white.webp","system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Psychic Power, Tier 3 &bull; Fate, Curse</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>2 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>2<br><strong>Range</strong> 1 within 12<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>7<br><strong>Duration&nbsp;</strong>Save ends<br><strong>Resist&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Potential 6)<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>For the duration of the effect, all 1s count as -2 successes, rather than -1.&nbsp;<br><strong>Augment 2&nbsp;</strong>Saving against this effect requires 3 successes.&nbsp;</p>","cost":2,"subType":"psychicPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.A46VWrP8k5d5io7U"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1770500759223,"modifiedTime":1774473634555,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"ZXB0FS0kmZKZyxBN"}
{"name":"Haste","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/time/clock-spinning-gold-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lVAE6xF1waF6XO3W"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-dba118be-7fff-29a1-f6b5-befa06c33f86\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tier 2 Psychic Power &bull; Time</span></strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Difficulty: 5</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cost: 2 Increments</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Target: 1 creature within 10</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Duration: 2 rounds</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Effect: The target gains 1 additional AP while the spell lasts. They also gain a +2 bonus to their Movement Speed and a +10 bonus to their Initiative value.</p>\n<p>Augment 2: The duration increases to 2+1d3 rounds.</p>\n<p>Augment 2: The bonuses to speed and initiative increase to +3 and +15, respectively.</p>","cost":2,"subType":"psychicPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774473638212,"modifiedTime":1774473638212,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"9crOAzEwpPuFsO2t"}
{"name":"Mass Haste","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/time/clock-spinning-gold-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.jbNapb5rkMKzkKCo"}},"system":{"tier":4,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-dba118be-7fff-29a1-f6b5-befa06c33f86\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tier 4 Psychic Power &bull; Time</span></strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Difficulty: 8</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cost: 3 Increments</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Target: Burst 3 within 16</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Duration: 2 rounds</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Effect: The target(s) gain 1 additional AP while the spell lasts. They also gain a +2 bonus to their Movement Speed and a +10 bonus to their Initiative value.</p>\n<p>Augment 2: The duration increases to 2+1d3 rounds.</p>\n<p>Augment 2: The bonuses to speed and initiative increase to +3 and +15, respectively.</p>","cost":2,"subType":"psychicPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769616351638,"modifiedTime":1774473642888,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"4SHUpR9lyjpyKsm6"}
{"name":"Mass Slow","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/time/clock-analog-gray.webp","system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-dba118be-7fff-29a1-f6b5-befa06c33f86\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tier 3 Psychic Power &bull; Time</span></strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Difficulty: 7<br>Cost: 2 Increment<br>Target: Burst 3 within 16<br>Duration: 2 rounds<br>Effect: The target(s) must make a D6 Potential save. On failure: the target loses 1 AP while the spell lasts. They also gain a -2 penalty to their Movement Speed and a -10 penalty to their Initiative value. This effect cannot decrease Movement Speed below 2 or Initiative below 0.<br>Augment 1: The duration changes to \"save ends\".<br>Augment 2: The resist difficulty is increased to D9.<br>Augment 2: The penalties to speed and initiative increase to -3 and -15, respectively.</p>","cost":0,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.hVrC5Uhz7Ch0oi31"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769530158279,"modifiedTime":1774473645625,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"cxEyeI2KSdk4nbVb"}
{"name":"Slow","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/time/clock-analog-gray.webp","system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-dba118be-7fff-29a1-f6b5-befa06c33f86\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tier 1 Psychic Power &bull; Time</span></strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Difficulty: 4</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cost: 1 Increment</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Target: 1 creature within 12</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Duration: 2 rounds</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Effect: The target must make a D4 Potential save. On failure: the target loses 1 AP while the spell lasts. They also gain a -2 penalty to their Movement Speed and a -10 penalty to their Initiative value. This effect cannot decrease Movement Speed below 2 or Initiative below 0.</p>\n<p>Augment 1: The duration changes to \"save ends\".</p>\n<p>Augment 2: The resist difficulty is increased to D7.</p>\n<p>Augment 2: The penalties to speed and initiative increase to -3 and -15, respectively.</p>","cost":0,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Jkh0qu5oKA35Kd7L"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769530158279,"modifiedTime":1774473647519,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"99R3D988KdGiTRF6"}
{"name":"Banish","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-hand-glow-pink.webp","system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Psychic Power, Tier 2 &bull; Void, Death</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range&nbsp;</strong>1 within 12<br><strong>Cost</strong> 2 Increments<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>6<br><strong>Resistance&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Stamina 4)<br><strong>Armor -<br>Effect&nbsp;</strong>The target must make a D4 Stamina save. On failure, it is banished to the Void and dies instantly.<br><strong>Augment 2&nbsp;</strong>The resist difficulty increases to 6.</p>","cost":2,"subType":"psychicPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.DAU8SUEUTopuAmJ2"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767476418998,"modifiedTime":1774473650826,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"bDboLiD8CfkqRvFN"}
{"name":"Implosion","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/unholy/orb-contained-pink.webp","system":{"tier":4,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Psychic Power, Tier 4 &bull; Void</strong></p>\n<p><em>A tiny portal to the void opens where the caster directs it to, sucking in the surrounding air as it expands, briefly reaching the size of a man before it collapses in on itself, blinking out of existence and taking whatever it swallowed with it.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Cost&nbsp;</strong>2 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>3<br><strong>Range</strong> Burst 10 within 30<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>7<br><strong>Resistance&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Stamina 8)<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>All targets within the burst must make a D8 Stamina resist; on failure, they are moved up to 5 m toward the center of the burst. <em>Secondary: </em>All targets within 3 m of the center take 200% Untyped damage. Any target(s) in the center square of the burst take 300% Untyped damage.&nbsp;<em>Tertiary:&nbsp;</em>Any target(s) in the center of the burst must make a D6 Stamina resist or be banished to the Void (this is a death effect).<br><strong>Augment 3</strong>: The range of the spell increases to Burst 12 within 36. The bursts for the secondary and tertiary effects increase to 7 and 3, respectively.<br><strong>Augment 2</strong>: The resist difficulty for the banishment effect incrases to D8.</p>","cost":2,"subType":"psychicPower","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":2},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.zCJbhqOtGiHiNrw2"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1770409381320,"modifiedTime":1774473654854,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"C6rwgVe9ztQKrhDB"}
{"name":"Piercing Silence","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/air/wind-vortex-swirl-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9SDQPC4G3UNzyoFg"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>Psychic Power, Tier 1</p>\n<p>Difficulty 5</p>\n<p>Cost: 2 Increments</p>\n<p>Target: Burst 3 within 10</p>\n<p>Effect: The target area becomes a zone of magical silence. While the spell is active, no-one within the zone may cast a spell or manifest a power. It is possible to brute-force the spell; a casting check over a difficulty of 8(/10/12) will break this spell.</p>","cost":2,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"psychic","damageMultiplier":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774473659440,"modifiedTime":1774473659440,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"x5MMTvf0zG0StA7K"}
{"name":"Crashing Wave","type":"power","img":"icons/magic/water/wave-water-blue.webp","system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 3 Martial Exploit &bull; Spear</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites&nbsp;</strong>You are wielding a polearm<strong><br>Cost&nbsp;</strong>2 Increments<br><strong>AP</strong> 3<br><strong>Range&nbsp;</strong>Weapon<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>+3<br><strong>Resist&nbsp;</strong>Yes (Stamina 6)<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>On hit: the target takes 200% damage and must make a D6 Stamina resist; on failure: the target is vaulted into the air, pushing it up to 3 squares. <em>Secondary: </em>You may make a secondary attack against the target to knock it back down at the same difficulty; on hit: the target takes 100% damage, ignoring armor, is knocked prone and must make a D6 Stamina resist; on failure: the target is stunned for one round.&nbsp;</p>","cost":2,"subType":"martialExploit","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"meleeWeapon","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"martial","damageMultiplier":2},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.2qdphkAhbP0cFeVn"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1770477908170,"modifiedTime":1774473677470,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"Y3yNVPgJie9knd9T"}
{"name":"Keep Your Distance","type":"power","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-polearm-glowing-white.webp","system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 2 Exploit &bull; Reaction, Immediate Interrupt</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Cost</strong> 1 Increment<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>Reaction<br><strong>Difficulty&nbsp;</strong>+2<br><strong>Prerequisites&nbsp;</strong>You are wielding a reach weapon<br><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>When a creature moves into your weapon reach, as a reaction: you may make an attack against it. On hit: it takes 100% damage and you push it up to one square away from you. This interrupts its movement.</p>","cost":0,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"catalyst","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"arcane","damageMultiplier":0},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.v95YfVMSA11WJcvc"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769812959642,"modifiedTime":1774473679168,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"Q8VaTdiGUhsNKrWQ"}
{"name":"Piercing Thrust","type":"power","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-polearm-light-orange.webp","system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Martial Power, Tier 2 &bull; Piercing</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Cost: </strong>2 Increments<br><strong>AP&nbsp;</strong>2<br><strong>Range:&nbsp;</strong>Weapon + 1<br><strong>Difficulty:&nbsp;</strong>+3<br><strong>Prerequisites:&nbsp;</strong>You are wielding a weapon that does piercing damage.<br><strong>Effect:&nbsp;</strong>You lunge forward, thrusting your weapon at a weak point in the enemy's armor. On hit: the target suffers 200% damage. The attack's Pen value is equal to the damage roll.</p>","cost":2,"subType":"arcaneSpell","requiresEquipment":true,"requiredEquipmentType":"meleeWeapon","requiredEquipmentSubtype":"arcane","characteristic":"martial","damageMultiplier":2},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.toNMjybp4z9tLgvi"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768682859611,"modifiedTime":1774473683814,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"Vl5TJiGxvP0x1DkO"}
